data.text: @harryillers oh no! Hope things get better soon!
@harryillers @JeremySzal Oh brilliant. I’m so glad - makes everything a little easier for you and for Squash xx
@harryillers I'm so sorry, I really hope she recovers, as I do all of you xx
@ELCrocker3 @harryillers Under The Skin but Isserley’s true form is a dachshund

@harryillers Get well soon! Do you have a blanket with the smell from the puppies and Mom? It really helped my dachshund Pablo getting used to his crate. Also, put a little dog basket in the crate. It helps them find an easier spot to sleep during the night. Best of luck! ❤️

@LouAllenJones Thank you so much. We put a calming playlist on and she slept much better, but sadly Rocket was very ill overnight and is going back to the vet this morning where it’s likely she’ll be admitted 😔
@JeremySzal @GillianRedfearn Put a dog calming Spotify playlist on last night and we had a much better night!
